        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px;">phone</span>
        +54 9 261 539-1110
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDXApJxCIqg9kKsjzschP3v6RmoEVEXf-XbUn5KA6iJPKmGwvq7letBZHZT-LbfHB8oJclAR4f1RHM_GmZ1LZrmlUVPy8fbXY11TXyjQSMmp5b9KtfYGugPKljJzR6YMzGfF0aVtyEelt49CteLEDyPl1QuIKWh6eUlWREeJkSz0HnDkZKB3xxmNrrO6vgM_M3XY1wnVBNPIfilhHCkt6Cj_Polmaji1uYM_SECA56FfZh-q9u1_93OhYhpt2hy8pHUFDcKB_aYN9E"
        alt="Cabina de aeronave con azafata profesional"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/45"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center py-16">

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div class="text-white animate-fade-in-up">
        <span class="inline-block bg-[#C4A456] text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm mb-6">
          Próximo inicio — Anotate ya
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-display mb-6">Tu carrera en las nubes comienza aquí.</h1>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-neutral-100 leading-relaxed" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          Curso de Tripulante de Cabina de Pasajeros (TCP) — Modalidad Presencial
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300 mb-10">
          Teoría y prácticas en Mendoza · Práctica de vuelo en Buenos Aires
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-5 text-sm text-neutral-200">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#C4A456]" style="font-size:20px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">verified</span>
            Título Oficial ANAC
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#C4A456]" style="font-size:20px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">location_on</span>
            100% Presencial
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#C4A456]" style="font-size:20px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">schedule</span>
            Inicio Próximamente
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Form card -->
      <div class="glass-panel p-7 md:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full md:max-w-md md:ml-auto animate-fade-in-up-delay-2">
        <h3 class="text-headline-md text-neutral-900 mb-1.5">Anotate al curso</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Dejanos tus datos y te contactamos por WhatsApp con toda la información y fecha de inicio.
        </p>

        <!-- Primary: WhatsApp CTA -->
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/5492615391110?text=Hola%2C+quiero+m%C3%A1s+informaci%C3%B3n+sobre+el+curso+de+TCP+(Tripulante+de+Cabina+de+Pasajeros)"
          target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-[#25D366] text-white py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm tracking-wider hover:bg-[#1ebe5d] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl mb-5"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
          </svg>
          QUIERO INSCRIBIRME
        </a>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-neutral-200"></div>
          <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-medium">o dejá tus datos</span>
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-neutral-200"></div>
        </div>

        <form class="space-y-3" id="lead-form">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1.5">Nombre Completo</label>
            <input type="text" name="nombre" placeholder="Ej. Ana García"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 bg-white text-neutral-900 placeholder-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C4A456] focus:border-transparent text-sm" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1.5">Teléfono / WhatsApp</label>
            <input type="tel" name="telefono" placeholder="+54 9 261 000-0000"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 bg-white text-neutral-900 placeholder-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C4A456] focus:border-transparent text-sm" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1.5">Ciudad</label>
            <input type="text" name="ciudad" placeholder="Mendoza"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 bg-white text-neutral-900 placeholder-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C4A456] focus:border-transparent text-sm" />
          </div>
          <button type="submit"
            class="w-full bg-[#D71920] text-white py-3.5 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm tracking-widest hover:bg-[#ae0011] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl mt-1">
            RECIBIR INFORMACIÓN
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== METODOLOGÍA ===== -->
  <section id="metodologia" class="py-24 bg-[#f3f4f5]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-headline-lg text-[#D71920] mb-4">Formación de Excelencia</h2>
        <div class="h-0.5 w-20 bg-[#C4A456] mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" id="programa">
        <div class="reveal-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm gold-gradient-border hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 opacity-0">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-[#C4A456]" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">location_city</span>
            <span class="text-6xl font-black text-neutral-100 leading-none select-none" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">01</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-headline-md mb-4">Formación Presencial</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Clases teóricas y prácticas acuáticas/terrestres en nuestras sedes de Mendoza. Prácticas de vuelo real coordinadas en Buenos Aires.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm gold-gradient-border hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 opacity-0" style="transition-delay:0.12s;">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-[#C4A456]" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">workspace_premium</span>
            <span class="text-6xl font-black text-neutral-100 leading-none select-none" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">02</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-headline-md mb-4">Aval ANAC</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Nuestro programa cumple con los más altos estándares internacionales y está avalado por la Administración Nacional de Aviación Civil.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal-card bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm gold-gradient-border hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 opacity-0" style="transition-delay:0.24s;">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-[#C4A456]" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">menu_book</span>
            <span class="text-6xl font-black text-neutral-100 leading-none select-none" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">03</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-headline-md mb-4">Currícula Completa</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Desde seguridad aérea y primeros auxilios hasta servicio a bordo de lujo y etiqueta internacional. Todo lo que necesitas para brillar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== POR QUÉ GOOD FLIGHT ===== -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">

      <div class="md:w-1/2 reveal-card opacity-0">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDuytKHfA8b_MJQPHzszRceVDlFmeeHyPDZ_SrSMSNrudnW7qFa_Kwxd6rFauWqkfs-yZl65vTETWSjbWMNXxjtOaLSy3hfVNefvGqXT5csJxQgrU_3lb-jSz3kJkOvlkiEZhi-F8ac2H8fVoDtdMcwtDYD4f5BdFUqiT-gxu7jn06erqkWlEIFyrCQj5J0C8Oc0t5gPFzfebTqNLMIOi8VaSiFVFzny2mjP-J9MZk8LuDKcQVTrhqGWFGesoHsgYdkk6yytjDynRI"
            alt="Instalaciones de entrenamiento Good Flight" class="w-full h-auto"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#C4A456]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-1/2 reveal-card opacity-0" style="transition-delay:0.15s;">
        <h2 class="text-headline-lg text-neutral-900 mb-5">¿Por qué elegir Good Flight?</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-lg mb-10 italic leading-relaxed" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          "Liderando la formación aeronáutica con trayectoria y excelencia académica en Mendoza."
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-7">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="bg-red-50 p-2.5 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#D71920]" style="font-size:22px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 block mb-1">Instructores Activos</span>
              <span class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Aprende de profesionales que operan actualmente en las aerolíneas más importantes del mundo.</span>
            </div>
